    <para id="id324502"><emphasis effect="italics">for all <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mi>k</m:mi><m:mo>∈</m:mo><m:mi mathvariant="bold">Z</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>. Summing over <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>ℓ</m:mi></m:math> gives</emphasis></para><equation id="uid46">
      <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
        <m:mrow>
          <m:munder>
            <m:mo>∑</m:mo>
            <m:mi>n</m:mi>
